snippet.title: Crystal Story - Awakening and Dawn of Dusk TEASER
snippet.description:
Play Crystal Story: Awakening:
https://bredfrown.itch.io/crystal-story

Follow Crystal Story development on Twitter:
https://twitter.com/thecrystalstory

It's been a while. These are challenging times and I hope you have been well. I will be working hard to present Crystal Story: Dawn of Dusk in late 2021. Stay tuned!
